WEBVTT

00:08:59.105 --> 00:09:01.166
So wherever the shadows are, it's night

00:09:01.190 --> 00:09:03.311
and wherever the sun is,
it's actually day.

00:09:04.453 --> 00:09:06.703
Time is this extraordinary thing

00:09:06.727 --> 00:09:09.338
that we never can really
wrap our heads around.

00:09:09.940 --> 00:09:11.942
But in a very unique and special way,

00:09:11.966 --> 00:09:15.798
I believe these photographs
begin to put a face on time.

00:09:16.703 --> 00:09:21.083
They embody a new
metaphysical visual reality.

00:09:22.996 --> 00:09:25.750
When you spend 15 hours
looking at a place,

00:09:26.917 --> 00:09:29.124
you're going to see things
a little differently

00:09:29.148 --> 00:09:31.156
than if you or I walked up
with our camera,